TI  - Towards a public multilingual knowledge management infrastructure for the European digital single market
AU  - Schmitz, P.
AU  - Francesconi, E.
AU  - Hajlaoui, N.
AU  - Batouche, B.
T2  - CEUR Workshop Proceedings
A2  - Declerck, T.
